gger=\"\"><svg role=\"progressbar\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Calendar &amp; Bookings</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Calendar &amp; Bookings</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">Book, view, and manage all your salon appointments in one place</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Calendar is where all your appointments live. It shows your team&#x27;s full schedule side by side — one column per staff member — so you can see everyone&#x27;s day at a glance and book new appointments in seconds.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"how-the-calendar-is-laid-out\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#how-the-calendar-is-laid-out\" class=\"peer\">How the Calendar is laid out</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>When you open the Calendar you&#x27;ll see:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A column for each staff member</strong> — each person has their own lane with their profile photo and name at the top</li>\n<li><strong>Time slots running down the page</strong> — the interval (15, 30, or 45 min) is set in <a href=\"/docs/settings#calendar\">Settings → Calendar</a></li>\n<li><strong>A red line showing the current time</strong> — so you always know where you are in the day</li>\n<li><strong>Appointment cards</strong> — each card shows the client name, service, and time range</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation bar at the top</strong> — use <strong>Today</strong>, <strong>&lt;</strong>, and <strong>&gt;</strong> to move between days, or click the date to jump to a specific day</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>The <strong>+ Add</strong> button in the top right corner is for selling products, memberships, or vouchers directly — it opens a cart where you select the items and a client. It is <strong>not</strong> for creating appointments. To book an appointment, click directly on an empty time slot in a staff column.</p></div></div></div>\n<p><img alt=\"Quick Sale Cart\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-lg\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 70vw, 900px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F4_appointment_cart.033iwcfuxep4i.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"booking-a-new-appointment\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#booking-a-new-appointment\" class=\"peer\">Booking a new appointment</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>To create an appointment, click on any <strong>empty time slot</strong> in a staff member&#x27;s column. A booking panel will slide open on the right side of the screen.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Booking an Appointment\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-lg\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 70vw, 900px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F1_appointment_booking.0et85s--glebi.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-1--select-a-client\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-1--select-a-client\" class=\"peer\">Step 1 — Select a client</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>The left side of the panel shows your client list. You can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search</strong> by name or phone number</li>\n<li>Select an <strong>existing client</strong> from the list</li>\n<li>Choose <strong>Walk-In Customer</strong> if the client isn&#x27;t registered</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Add new client</strong> to create a new profile on the spot</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>You don&#x27;t need to pre-register a client. Walk-In Customer works perfectly for first-time or unregistered visitors.</p></div></div></div>\n<p>Once you select a client, their name, phone, and email will be confirmed on screen. You can click <strong>Change Client</strong> if you need to swap to someone else, or <strong>View [Client]&#x27;s Profile</strong> to open their full history.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-2--add-services\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-2--add-services\" class=\"peer\">Step 2 — Add services</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>On the right side of the panel, click <strong>+ Add service</strong>. A service picker will open showing all your available services with their price and duration.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tick the <strong>checkbox</strong> next to any service you want to add</li>\n<li>You can select multiple services at once</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Done</strong> when you&#x27;re finished</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The selected services appear in the <strong>Appointment</strong> panel showing the time, duration, assigned team, and price. The total updates automatically at the bottom.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-3--save\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-3--save\" class=\"peer\">Step 3 — Save</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Click <strong>Save</strong>. The appointment is created instantly and appears as a card on the calendar. A green <strong>&quot;Appointment created successfully&quot;</strong> notification will confirm it.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"appointment-card-hover\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#appointment-card-hover\" class=\"peer\">Appointment card hover</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Hover over any appointment card on the calendar to see a quick summary popup showing:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The time range (e.g., 14:30 – 15:30)</li>\n<li>The current status badge (e.g., <strong>Scheduled</strong>)</li>\n<li>The client&#x27;s name and phone number</li>\n<li>The service name, team, duration, and price</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"editing-an-appointment\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#editing-an-appointment\" class=\"peer\">Editing an appointment</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Click on an existing appointment card to open the <strong>Edit Appointment</strong> panel. It works the same as the booking panel — you can change the client, add or remove services, or update the time or Status.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Managing Appointment Status\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-lg\" style=\"color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 70vw, 900px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F2_appointment_status.0vxxplhf-lxpf.gif&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></p>\n<p>At the top of the edit panel you&#x27;ll see status action buttons:</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Button</th><th>What it does</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Arrived</strong></td><td>Marks the client as checked in and present</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Start</strong></td><td>Marks the service as actively in progress</td></tr><tr><td><strong>No Show</strong></td><td>Records that the client didn&#x27;t show up</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Cancel</strong></td><td>Cancels the appointment</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>The status is reflected both on the appointment card and in the hover popup.</p>\n<p>At the bottom of the panel you&#x27;ll see two buttons:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Save</strong> — saves any changes you made</li>\n<li><strong>Checkout</strong> — moves the appointment to the payment screen to collect payment</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"appointment-statuses\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#appointment-statuses\" class=\"peer\">Appointment statuses</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>What it means</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Scheduled</td><td>The appointment is booked and upcoming</td></tr><tr><td>Arrived</td><td>The client has arrived at the salon</td></tr><tr><td>Start</td><td>The service is currently in progress</td></tr><tr><td>No Show</td><td>The client didn&#x27;t show up</td></tr><tr><td>Cancelled</td><td>The appointment was cancelled</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"blocking-time-off\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#blocking-time-off\" class=\"peer\">Blocking time off</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Need to mark a staff member as unavailable for a break, training, or any other reason? You can block out time without creating a real appointment.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click on an empty time slot in a staff member&#x27;s column and select <strong>Block Time</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set the start time, end time, and an optional note so the team knows why the slot is blocked.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>. The blocked slot will appear as a distinct card on the calendar.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"going-to-checkout-from-the-calendar\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#going-to-checkout-from-the-calendar\" class=\"peer\">Going to checkout from the calendar</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Once a client&#x27;s appointment is done, you can take payment directly from the calendar.</p>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click on the appointment card to open the Edit Appointment panel.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Checkout</strong> at the bottom of the panel.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>The payment screen opens with the services already loaded. Follow the <a href=\"/docs/checkout\">Checkout</a> steps to apply discounts, add a tip, and collect payment.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"quick-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#quick-reference\" class=\"peer\">Quick reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>How it works</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Staff columns</td><td>One column per team member with their photo</td></tr><tr><td>Date navigation</td><td>Use Today, &lt;, and &gt; buttons to change the day</td></tr><tr><td>Walk-in booking</td><td>Select &quot;Walk-In Customer&quot; — no profile needed</td></tr><tr><td>Multiple services</td><td>Tick as many services as needed in the service picker</td></tr><tr><td>Appointment statuses</td><td>Arrived, Start, No Show, Cancel — updated from the edit panel</td></tr><tr><td>Hover card</td><td>Hover an appointment to see a quick summary without opening it</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/dashboard\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Dashboard</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A real-time overview of your salon&#x27;s performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/checkout\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Checkout</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Collect payment, print receipts, and manage completed sales</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M17 19H3\"></path></svg>On this page</h3><div class=\"relative min-h-0 text-sm ms-px overflow-auto [scrollbar-width:none] mask-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,white_16px,white_calc(100%-16px),transparent)] py-3\"><div class=\"relative\"><div data-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 bg-fd-primary w-px transition-[clip-path]\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(0 var(--fd-top), 100% var(--fd-top), 100% calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)), 0 calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)))\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col border-s border-fd-foreground/10\"><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#how-the-calendar-is-laid-out\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">How the Calendar is laid out</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#booking-a-new-appointment\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Booking a new appointment</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-1--select-a-client\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 1 — Select a client</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-2--add-services\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 2 — Add services</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-3--save\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 3 — Save</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#appointment-card-hover\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Appointment card hover</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#editing-an-appointment\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Editing an appointment</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#appointment-statuses\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Appointment statuses</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#blocking-time-off\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Blocking time off</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#going-to-checkout-from-the-calendar\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Going to checkout from the calendar</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#quick-reference\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Quick reference</a></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ivik3ip_mfgc.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[67028,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_b-80nser09y.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/02xrdmooo78xa.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.ibz23cej6~d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.0hv6s5x-q5..js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/09o9g~xg2p.-q.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0g3_p-i~mr1nu.js\\\"],\\\"Provider\\\"]\\n3:I[32961,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_b-80nser09y.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/02xrdmooo78xa.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.ibz23cej6~d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.0hv6s5x-q5..js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/09o9g~xg2p.-q.js\\\",\\\"/_next/stat